2022 Was a fairytale and a nightmare all wrapped into one. 
Heres to 2023 my friends! ❤️
#newyear #newyears #gamergirl #egirl #model #modeling #twitch #twitchstreamer #twitchaffiliate #happyholidays #2022 #2023

While 2022 is coming to an end, 
I feel like I must say some words…❤️❤️❤️
This was the year, 
I caught myself on fire…🔥
Got to go to TwitchCon all because of my beautiful Serena Kingdom…😍
Saw Giraffes for the first TIME ever (I thought they were fake.)🦒
Networked and meet so MANY amazing content creators across so many different platforms… LOVE YALL NEW PALS! 💓
Pushed myself out of my comfort zone…💙
Went to my First ever Pride Event🌈
…. And one of the hardest things this year…
I lost my best friend Zero, my childhood pet….
We also lost my grandmas weenie dog, Rojo, and a cat that was dumped at our house many years ago, Scar, I love and miss them all very much… 
With this year being a world wind of emotions I just want to say to those who have stuck around, I love you, and thank you for being my friend. 
For this New Year, My Goals are to continue to work on myself as a person, apply to the sponsorships of my dreams, take breaks when needed, and to always remember to be kind! 
I will continue streaming on Twitch, posting to Youtube, and being as active as I possibly can here! 
Y’all have a Happy New Year, and stay safe! ✨🪩💯❤️
